1.00	Mister_Vampire	Mr. Vampire	Mr Vampire is a 1985 Hong Kong comedy horror film directed by Ricky Lau and produced by Sammo Hung. The film's box office success led to the creation of a Mr. Vampire franchise, with the release of four sequels directed by Ricky Lau from 1986 to 1992, and subsequent similarly themed films with different directors released between 1987 and 1991. The film was released under the Chinese title 暫時停止呼吸 (literally: Hold Your Breath for a Moment) in Taiwan.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/04/MrVampirePoster.jpg/220px-MrVampirePoster.jpg
